[31m-[m
[31m-## Viewport Units[m
[31m-[m
[31m-```css[m
[31m-/* Standard viewport units */[m
[31m-.full-height {[m
[31m-  height: 100vh; /* May cause issues on mobile */[m
[31m-}[m
[31m-[m
[31m-/* Dynamic viewport units (recommended for mobile) */[m
[31m-.full-height-dynamic {[m
[31m-  height: 100dvh; /* Accounts for mobile browser UI */[m
[31m-}[m
[31m-[m
[31m-/* Small viewport (minimum) */[m
[31m-.min-full-height {[m
[31m-  min-height: 100svh;[m
[31m-}[m
[31m-[m
[31m-/* Large viewport (maximum) */[m
[31m-.max-full-height {[m
[31m-  max-height: 100lvh;[m
[31m-}[m
[31m-[m
[31m-/* Viewport-relative font sizing */[m
[31m-.hero-title {[m
[31m-  /* 5vw with min/max bounds */[m
[31m-  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);[m
[31m-}[m
[31m-```[m
[31m-[m
[31m-## Best Practices[m
[31m-[m
[31m-1. **Mobile-First**: Start with mobile styles, enhance for larger screens[m
[31m-2. **Content Breakpoints**: Set breakpoints based on content, not devices[m
[31m-3. **Fluid Over Fixed**: Use fluid values for typography and spacing[m
[31m-4. **Container Queries**: Use for component-level responsiveness[m
[31m-5. **Test Real Devices**: Simulators don't catch all issues[m
[31m-6. **Performance**: Optimize images, lazy load off-screen content[m
[31m-7. **Touch Targets**: Maintain 44x44px minimum on mobile[m
[31m-8. **Logical Properties**: Use inline/block for internationalization[m
[31m-[m
[31m-## Common Issues[m
[31m-[m
[31m-- **Horizontal Overflow**: Content breaking out of viewport[m
[31m-- **Fixed Widths**: Using px instead of relative units[m
[31m-- **Viewport Height**: 100vh issues on mobile browsers[m
[31m-- **Font Size**: Text too small on mobile[m
[31m-- **Touch Targets**: Buttons too small to tap accurately[m
[31m-- **Aspect Ratio**: Images squishing or stretching[m
[31m-- **Z-Index Stacking**: Overlays breaking on different screens[m
[31m-[m
[31m-## Resources[m
[31m-[m
[31m-- [CSS Container Queries](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_container_queries)[m
[31m-- [Utopia Fluid Type Calculator](https://utopia.fyi/type/calculator/)[m
[31m-- [Every Layout](https://every-layout.dev/)[m
[31m-- [Responsive Images Guide](https://web.dev/responsive-images/)[m
[31m-- [CSS Grid Garden](https://cssgridgarden.com/)[m
